  "texts": [
    "For a comprehensive overview of tools and advice related to connectivity and synchronization, we refer to the article by Niehorster et al. (2025).",
    "This list can be seen as questions researchers can ask themselves and decide whether they are relevant to their particular research context.",
    "We will elaborate on some of these questions later in the article.",
    "Other considerations may be directly related to the research question and participant group, for instance:",
    "Where humans look in the world."
